### 禁止连接询问
StrictHostKeyChecking no
### 定时心跳
ServerAliveInterval 60
HostKeyAlgorithms +ssh-rsa

### 连接复用
#ControlMaster     auto
#ControlPath       ~/.ssh/control-%C
#ControlPersist    yes


